name: Christina Archer
coverLetter: Aloha! I've been trimming for a few years of outdoor. I'm looking for a place to park the car and maybe place a tent with my brother and friend. We are coming from Ohio and are looking for work right away, we don't drink or smoke and are available as long as you have us. We can supply our own food.  Please contact by phone: 440-665-4616, can't wait to hear from you :)
